    public class UnitBool
extends UnitObjectConst<BaseBoolIF>
implements UnitBoolIF
    This class represents 'UnitBool' objects and is used for 'MovingBool' objects with a constant boolean value over a certain period of time.
    Author:
    Markus Fuessel
